+/*
+ * rtl8187b specific rfkill support
+ *
+ * NOTE: we only concern about two states
+ *   eRfOff: RFKILL_STATE_SOFT_BLOCKED
+ *   eRfOn: RFKILL_STATE_UNBLOCKED
+ * TODO: move led controlling source code to rfkill framework
